column5: Off to a good start... First day fishing musky this year my buddy cracked a 48 incher on the cast.... Did a huge tail walk...  Awesome fight...
Good one. That's some freaky green clouds in the ground. Haha
Sweet.  It's always good to land the first one.   Congrats on a great catch.
Beauty Mike, congrats to your bud
nice fish, i think i know that spot
Great catch, especially for the first of the year! Nice oil painting, too.
Nice fish. Good looking markings on that girl.
Dang, I was hoping to get to the painting before anyone else!  Beauty!!!!!
Thanks everyone...  My buddy was shaking for a while he was so pumped....
Beauty fish!! Way to start the season!!!
Awesome coloration on that Larry skie!  RJ
